kSources/978-0-306-80327-7\">978-0-306-80327-7</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Blues+from+the+Delta&amp;rft.place=New+York%2C+N.Y.&amp;rft.pub=Da+Capo+Press&amp;rft.date=1984&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-306-80327-7&amp;rft.au=Ferris%2C+William+R.&amp;rft.au=Taylor%2C+Billy&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWilliam+R.+Ferris\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.blues.org/halloffame/inductees.php4?ArtistId=23\">Blues Hall of Fame Inductees: Blues from the Delta - Dr. William Ferris.</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://finding-aids.lib.unc.edu/20367/\">\"William R. Ferris Collection, 1910s-2016\"</a>. <i>finding-aids.lib.unc.edu</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-11-06</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=finding-aids.lib.unc.edu&amp;rft.atitle=William+R.+Ferris+Collection%2C+1910s-2016&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ffinding-aids.lib.unc.edu%2F20367%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWilliam+R.+Ferris\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=William_R._Ferris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120229154825/http://www.neh.gov/news/archive/19970000a.html\">NEH bio</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://history.unc.edu/People/ferris.html\">University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill faculty page</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.folkstreams.net/filmmaker,65\">Folkstreams film page</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lib.unc.edu/mss/inv/f/Ferris,William_R.html\">William R. Ferris Collection</a>, Southern Folklife Collection, University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-top: 5px solid #bebebe;\">Government offices\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/wiki/Sheldon_Hackney\" title=\"Sheldon Hackney\">Sheldon Hackney</a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/wiki/Chair_of_the_National_Endowment_for_the_Humanities\" title=\"Chair of the National Endowment for the Humanities\">Chairperson</a> of the <a href=\"/wiki/National_Endowment_for_the_Humanities\" title=\"National Endowment for the Humanities\">National Endowment for the Humanities</a></b><br />1997\u20132001\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/wiki/Bruce_Cole\" title=\"Bruce Cole\">Bruce Cole</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Authority_control_frameless_&amp;#124;text-top_&amp;#124;10px_&amp;#124;alt=Edit_this_at_Wikidata_&amp;#124;link=https&amp;#58;//www.wikidat